<p>
Adds <a href="https://kotl.in/docs/spring-compiler-plugin">Spring Kotlin compiler plugin</a> to project build files:
</p>
<p>
Kotlin has classes and their members <code>final</code> by default, which makes it inconvenient to use frameworks
and libraries that require classes to be <code>open</code>.
</p>
<p>
The <code>kotlin-spring</code> compiler plugin adapts Kotlin to the requirements of the Spring framework and makes classes
annotated with a Spring-specific annotation and their members opened without the explicit <code>open</code> keyword.
</p>
